(77565, 307452, 7004, 4, '青春一根毛', '這首歌是當兵時休假在家寫的。放假在家，書沒念幾頁，吉他練起「島嶼天光」，只是又想到一些事情，於是就開始寫歌，當第一句哼出來以後，整曲很快就一氣呵成了。如果你也喜歡搖滾樂隊，我希望你可以從中想到屬於自己的故事。\n\n獻給一位大學室友。', '2014-04-01 00:00:00', 2000, 8, 0, 7, '「......如果不能重來，那麼，那就已經是最美好、最美好的事。」\n－－林達陽《慢情書》\n\n青春那四年，剩下最後一根毛\n你從哪裡帶一點給我\n\n難吃豆花店，異國明信片 \n練吉他長繭的指尖\n\n一張票根，兩種想念\n躺在錢包偶爾被發覺\n洗衣粉都，倒到池面\n風雨走廊的深夜\n\n一張票根，兩種想念\n搖滾樂隊的表演\n酒瓶砸碎，辜負少年\n有一天開始聽張懸\n\n我喚不回喚不回也學不會\n我喚不回喚不回也學不會\n\n青春那四年，剩下最後一根毛\n回不去，就是最好的紀念', '', 143, '', '', '', '', '大蘿蔔唱片行', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-07-18 12:43:54', '2015-03-12 14:08:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(77566, 6656, 7030, 1, '藤', '', '2014-07-18 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 17, '邦查語  Pangcah Language：\nyona mi hlu ngut ga mi e ludook\nmasa jugajuk jugajuk   ma sa jugajuk jugajuk   a why gwu lalan\nsa ju mumu mumuk   sa ju mumu mumuk   sa ju mumu mumuk   sado ga mi\nejuwa ay gia hlu ngut ha ge niy\nga gelim gelim gelim   ga gelim gelim gelim   ga gelim gelim gelim   sado gagwu\nneng han mi gafit ay r falerh no gilang\n\nda deng deng deng deng deng deng   han nagwu\ndanu jega sado gwu daruhlwuuh agwu\nana gukh～ana gukh～ana gukh～ana gukh～ \n\nmaligloon do gida ani niy   dalumaah do gida\nwu saba hmek ji ena an gwuniyan\n\nay ya san ji ena  wu wuwhy ma amin\nejuwa ay gia hlu ngut hageya\nejuwa ay gia hlu ngut   ejuwa ay gia hlu ngut\nedira ay ho elwudook ma amin\n\n漢譯：\n當我們在山裡採藤芯的時候\n一直往上爬    一直往上爬   無路可循\n我們鑽來鑽去    鑽來鑽去\n這藤芯到底在哪兒\n我努力的找著    我努力的找著   找著 \n原來它是攀附在樹梢上\n\n我不停的將它拉下    不停的拉下來\n搞得手指全都是刺\n好痛～好痛～好痛啊～\n\n現在我們要下山了    我們要回家了\n這是要給媽媽的一個驚喜\n\n媽媽說哎呀～怎麼都是藤條\n藤芯在哪裡   \n藤芯在哪裡    藤芯在哪裡\n全部都還留在山裡面\n\nLyrics mean：\nWhen I was a child, I plucked the rattan in the mountains.\nI could sell the picked rattan to help my mother with financial burdens.\nIt was not easy to pick the rattan.\nCuts on your hands were the price you had to pay.\nI was too young to distinguish which part of the rattan was useful.\nI didn’t realize I made a mistake until I went home.\nI left all the pith in the mountains and took the useless parts home.\nIt was an interesting childhood.\n', '', 232, '', '', '', '', '武藝音樂', '', 1, 1, 0, '2014-07-18 17:39:11', '2015-03-12 14:08:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(77567, 6656, 7030, 2, '遠洋', '', '2014-07-18 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 17, '邦查語  Pangcah Language：\n( miliyas sado gami do lumaah\ndaira e rumaay ah riyaarre mi fuding sado gami ah nini )\n\nraay raay sado ga mi do lumaah\nmaraay maraay sa do gwu lumaah nuniyam\nsawali sawali sado ga mi ah ni ni \nbasawali basawali sado ga mi ah ni ni\n( liyas liyas miliyas )\n\nmiliyas sado gami do lumaah\ndaira e rumaay ah riyaarre mi fuding sado gami ah nini\n( liyas miliyas )\n\nwu gadalaou an nu dawu ah riyaarre edira\nmalasawarh gina direng hagiya\nwurip nu mifuding gwuniyan hagiya\n( liyas liyas miliyas )\n\n漢譯：\n( 現在我們就離開家   前往未知的海域捕魚去 )\n\n我們離家    越來越遠    越來越遠\n我們的家也離我們    越來越遠   越來越遠\n現在我們向著東方    遷移    遷移\n我們現在一直航向東方    航向東方\n( 離開  離開  離開了 )\n\n現在我們就離開家    前往未知的海域捕魚去\n( 離開  離開了 )\n\n那是令人害怕的未知海域\n生命會不會就在這裡消失\n難道這就是捕魚人的命運\n( 離開  離開  離開了 )\n\nLyrics mean：\nYoung male aboriginals go oversea fishing and leave their homes miles away to earn their living.\nFear, dread, unknowns keep appearing.\nThis is the destiny of a fisherman.\n', '', 248, '', '', '', '', '武藝音樂', '', 1, 1, 0, '2014-07-18 17:40:44', '2015-03-12 14:08:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(77568, 6656, 7030, 3, '板模工人', '', '2014-07-18 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 17, '邦查語  Pangcah Language：\nwu mi mugung ay gwu da yaar nu niyam e babudar\n\nsarumiarrh bajihlar mi sa wuraarh ay e babudar\nsarumiaarh ma da yaar awaay gu hefung gu mimugung ay\ndaini do gura douge mi jurrz jurrz e da mi ya nan\nmagalah magalah gwu da yaar ma 心臟病\ndainian gwu daousi jejai gwu wuwak\nsalibahak do rumiarrh rumiarrh hai\ndani an gu dahga   dwusa an gu wuwak\nsalibahak do ga mi  awaay gu daramanai\nah heradeng nuniyam ah mafi rang\n\nhe yo in hoy yan naruwan hai yan ho in hoy yan\nhe yo ho wan hai yan ho wan hai yan ho in hoy yan\nhe yo ho wan hai yan ho wan hai yan ho wan hai yan\nhe yo ho wan hai yo an ho ay yan he yo ho wan\nhe yeh yo ho na lu wan   ho wan hai yan\nyeh yo ho na lu wan   heyo ho na lu wan   ho wan hai yan\n\n\n漢譯：\n我們的工作是在外面釘板模的工人\n\n在外面每天曝曬在太陽下和大雨中工作\n每天工作工作    沒有休假的板模工人\n那個老闆又來催我們趕工了\n趕趕趕    趕工趕得心臟病\n把喝的拿來    先乾一杯\n就會快樂    每一天    每一天\n把吃的拿來    再乾兩杯\n我們盡情的歡樂    我們沒有太多的想法\n去抱怨和生氣\n\n吼嗨呦 娜魯彎 ( 情緒虛詞 )\n\nLyrics mean：\nAboriginals leave their hometown for the city.\nWithout higher education and professional training, they can only work at construction sites as manual workers to earn their living.\nNo matter how harsh the sun is or how heavy the rain is, the merciless boss always makes us to work hard to meet a deadline.\nEvery day is so exhausting that we might get a heart attack.\nWe console each other through drinking together after work.\n', '', 260, '', '', '', '', '武藝音樂', '', 1, 1, 0, '2014-07-18 17:42:26', '2015-03-12 14:08:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(77569, 6656, 7030, 4, '女朋友', '', '2014-07-18 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 17, '邦查語  Pangcah Language：\nja ay sa gu ma an   sa ma nen han do   ay～ya～ya～  \nja ay sa gu ma an   han ha do ge ra    ay～ya～ya～  \n \nha na ki naah   ha na ki naah  na aye ga gwu   a～ya～ya～ya～ \nha na ki naah   ha na ki naah   ga wu sian   a～ya～ya～ya～ \nsa ru mi arh   hlih gu elu mah   jaay ga da yar\nru ray gu ma an\nsa ru mi arh   sa fgla elu mah   mi sa a rou ay\nma an sa gu ni yan\nwulah ne ma   be liy ah ni ma  ma la gwulung  ja ay ba juli\nla liuw wun gu ma ma   fafa he gu ayaw \nwu li san do ena   hla hli bis gu ayaw\nsa ma nen gu ni yan   我愛女朋友 \nwulah nu ma gu   sa ma nen\n\n漢譯：\n誰說不是這樣   那要怎麼樣   啊呀呀～\n誰說不是這樣   那就這樣啊   啊呀呀～ \n \n啊呦喂呀    啊呦喂呀   我不要這樣的    啊呀呀呀～\n啊呦喂呀    啊呦喂呀   討人厭的    啊呀呀呀～\n一整天    都窩在家   什麼事也不做\n累什麼累啦   \n一整天    都在家發呆   做白日夢\n這是要怎樣 \n是誰愛的    是誰要的   甘做牛馬   不敢吭一聲\n爸爸丟一旁    女朋友放前面\n叫娘閃一邊    愛人擺前面\n這要怎麼辦呢    我愛女朋友\n我就是喜歡    怎麼辦  \n\nLyrics mean：\nThere are many guys who forget their family as soon as they have girlfriends.\nThey will do anything for the girls to make them happy.\nIs it Chalaw''s story?\n', '', 291, '', '', '', '', '武藝音樂', '', 1, 1, 0, '2014-07-18 17:43:59', '2015-03-12 14:08:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(77570, 6656, 7030, 5, '不要勉強', '', '2014-07-18 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 17, '邦查語  Pangcah Language：\nmi su gu mi su   ma gu gu ma gu\nja ay yay ga lejarrh gu du aas nu mida\nnga lay du ma an   na ay du ma an\nwu ru ma ay gu be be liyyh nu mi da\na ga be ba ji ji  a ga be ba ji ji  du nu mi su ay ah wulaah\na ga be ba ji ji  a ga be ba ji ji  e ra gu nu magu ah wulaah   hay～yeh～yeh～\nwu～wu～   a ga be ba ji ji   wu～wu～   `ni maan mi ba ji ji\n\nja ay ga lejarrh gi da   era gu nu magu ah heradeng\nja ay ga lejarrh gi da   ah ga be ba ji ji e dagu wanan\nna mu gu na mu   ma gu gu ma gu\nah ga be ba ji ji   hay～yeh～yeh～\n\nah ga be ba ji ji nimaan mi ba ji ji e dagu wanan\nwu ru ma ay damhlaou gida    wu ru ma ay ah heradeng\nnimaan era gu malijarrh hlai ah hlimaak hagiya\nah ga be ba ji ji nimaan mi ba ji ji e dagu wanan\nwu ru ma ay damhlaou gida    wu ru ma ay ah heradeng\nnimaan era gu malijarrh hlai ah hlimaak hagiya\nwu ru ma ay damhlaou gida    wu ru ma ay ah heradeng\nnimaan era gu malijarrh hlai ah hlimaak hagiya\nwu～wu～   aga be ba ji ji\n\n\n漢譯：\n你走你的    我走我的\n我們成長的環境有所不同\n想要什麼    不要什麼\n我們會有不同的選擇\n不要勉強    不要勉強我    去接受你的方式\n不要勉強    不要勉強    我有我自己的喜好   嘿～耶～耶～\n嗚～ 嗚～   不要勉強    嗚～ 嗚～   為什麼要勉強\n\n我們是不一樣的   我有我自己的想法\n我們是不一樣的   不要再來勉強我\n你們是你們    我就是我\n不要勉強    嘿～耶～耶～\n\n不要勉強    為何要一直勉強我\n我們是不同的個體    有不同的思想\n怎麼可能會有一樣的結果\n不要勉強    幹嘛一直要勉強我\n我們是不同的個體    有不同的思想\n怎麼可能會有一樣的想法\n我們是不同的個體    有不同的思想\n怎麼可能會有一樣的想法\n嗚～ 嗚～   不要勉強\n\nLyrics mean：\nYou can’t force someone to be in a relationship.\nAs for the hero in this story, Chalaw, is married, so it’s not appropriate to make his story public.\n', '', 261, '', '', '', '', '武藝音樂', '', 1, 1, 0, '2014-07-18 17:45:41', '2015-03-12 14:08:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(77571, 6656, 7030, 6, '安慰', '', '2014-07-18 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 17, '邦查語  Pangcah Language：\nwu be dala agwu ga daini yan esu wu sabi he noom an   edagwu wa nan\nwu libahak sanu magwu mila yaab do ga daini esu\nmadiyado wumi sasuwar an eda era e ayaw\nera e wurip ah gwu gisu\nhai yeh hai yeh hai yo yan  hai yeh hai yeh hai yo yan\n\nah nu maraay gwu lalan e rigwurre era e dadihe esu gawu\nda nga sa e ga doas san esu gwu wulaah ah gwu\n\nah waay gwu dolaas\nhai yeh hai yeh hai yo yan   hai yeh hai yeh hai yo yan\nwu sabe he noom an   wu sabe he noom an   wu sabe he noom an\ne dagwuwanan   e dagwuwanan   e dagwuwanan\n\n\n漢譯：（查勞給女兒的歌）\n我的等待    你的到來    這是對我最安慰的事\n我滿心歡喜    迎接你的到來\n就好像我們以前就約定好的一樣\n你來到我的生命裡\n嗨耶嗨耶嗨呦洋    嗨耶嗨耶嗨呦洋  ( 歌詠虛詞 )\n\n未來的路雖然很遙遠    我會在你身邊一直陪著你\n我的愛會一直陪你到成年\n\n不會間斷\n嗨耶嗨耶嗨呦洋    嗨耶嗨耶嗨呦洋  ( 歌詠虛詞 )\n這是對我最安慰的事    這是對我最安慰的事   這是對我最安慰的事\n在我這裡    在我這裡    在我這裡\n\nLyrics mean：\nA warm song was written for and dedicated his daughter.\nWhen he was waiting for his daughter to be born, he got very emotional.\nEven though there is a long road ahead, Father’s love would accompany her forever.\n', '', 338, '', '', '', '', '武藝音樂', '', 1, 1, 0, '2014-07-18 17:49:52', '2015-03-12 14:08:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(77572, 6656, 7030, 7, 'A LI AH 姊夫啊', '', '2014-07-18 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 17, '邦查語  Pangcah Language：\nja ahles sagu jihlar   ma jajak gu da ngar\nma warak do gami   ma warak ma warak do ga mi\nmarurai  marurai marurai do ga mi\nma ejhang do ga mi   ma ejhang   ma ejhang do ga mi\n\nge lihlung ho geda A LI AH～  ba han han ho geda A LI AH～A LI AH～A LI AH～\n\nga duwan do gaduwan do way～\n\nmi limek   mi limek   do ga mi e la anu mi gelihlung\nsa maneg dara ja ahles gina jihlar a ni ni   A LI AH～A LI AH～hi～\nba han han   ba han han ho gida   A LI AH～\nhefang en   hefang en   ho gu di reng   nu mida\nah～～ah～ah～ah～ah～ah～ah～ah～ wei～\n\n漢譯：\n太陽真刺人    頭都快被煮熟\n我們就像中毒一樣    中毒    中毒    我們快要中毒\n累了累了    我們真的累了\n我們快被曬乾    曬乾    曬乾    我們快被曬乾了\n\n姊夫阿～我們先去乘涼好嗎   \n姊夫阿～我們休息一下好嗎    姊夫阿～姊夫阿～\n\n走吧    走吧    走了吧～\n\n躲起來    躲起來    我們到樓下躲太陽\n沒辦法太陽現在實在太刺人了    姊夫阿～姊夫阿～\n姊夫阿～休息一下    我們休息一下\n讓我們的身體    放鬆一下    放鬆一下吧\n阿～阿～阿～\n\nLyrics mean：\nThe sun is blazing in the middle of the day.\nThe top of my head seems to be boiling.\nThe toilsome work makes me feel poisoned.\nMy brother in law is a desperate workaholic.\nI advise him to take a rest!\nLet’s take a rest in a shaded place!\n\n', '', 294, '', '', '', '', '武藝音樂', '', 1, 1, 0, '2014-07-18 17:53:48', '2015-03-12 14:08:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(77573, 6656, 7030, 8, '什麼都沒有', '', '2014-07-18 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 17, '邦查語  Pangcah Language：\nmaan gwu maan era gwu maan ah wa ay gwu maan\nera gwu maan   ah waay gwu maan   hay yeh～ hay yeh～ hay yeh～\n\nwu maan gwu era ay\nahwaay gwu behla samanen ge na direng\nah waay gwu dan   ah waay gwu dan   ah waay gwu dan   ah waay gwu dan\nwu maan gwu libahakan\nera gwu maan ah waay gwu maan   ah waay ah waay ah waay\n\nwu maan gwu riharay an\nwu maan gwu maan era gwu maan\nah waay gwu dan   ah waay gwu dan   ah waay gwu dan   ah waay gwu dan\nlaliuw an nu fafahe dalajuwa do han gini\nah waay gwu   dan ah waay gwu dan   dan ah waay gwu dan   dan ah waay gwu dan\nera gwu maan ah waay gwu maan   ah waay ah waay ah waay\nera gwu maan ah waay gwu maan  hay yeh～ hay yeh～ hay yeh～\nhay yeh～ hay yeh～ hay yeh～\n\ntsy mora fameloman aine eia\nhanao akory ny hataoe\nmahantra tsy misy ho hane e ia\nvolar o maha rangahy e\n\n漢譯：\n到底有什麼    擁有什麼    失去了什麼\n擁有什麼    失去了什麼\n \n到底還擁有些什麼呢\n沒有錢    這生活該怎麼辦\n沒賺到錢    沒賺到錢    沒賺到錢    沒賺到錢\n有什麼好高興的\n擁有什麼    失去了什麼    沒了    沒了    什麼都沒了\n\n有什麼    好輕鬆的\n到底還能做什麼    還有些什麼\n賺沒有錢    賺沒有錢\n太太跑了    到底是去了哪裡\n沒賺錢    沒賺到錢\n還有什麼    失去了什麼    沒了    沒了    什麼都沒了\n擁有什麼    失去了什麼 \n\n生活不是那麼容易\n我該怎麼做\n貧窮到沒錢吃飯\n金錢讓人有所做為\n\nLyrics mean：\nIt is a terrible feeling to not have money.\nEverything is a problem if one has no money.\nPeople should not let themselves be trapped in this situation.\nFriends leave when one doesn’t have money.\nWives run away when one doesn’t have money.\nPeople can’t speak up if they don’t have money.\n\nIt’s not easy to find a way to live.\nWhat shall I do.\nPoor and nothing to eat.\nMoney make you somebody.\n', '', 243, '', '', '', '', '武藝音樂', '', 1, 1, 0, '2014-07-18 17:57:30', '2015-03-12 14:08:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
